          <Vi>trên, ở phần trên, cao hơn</Vi>
          <En>being in or coming from the higher part or position; situated above</En>
          <Example>She placed the book on the upper shelf.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
